      "content": "but that's just easy for you to say. what does \"worth\" even matter when you're looking at a mountain of debt that will take decades to clear? i feel like i'm just waiting for the inevitable. the more i think about it, the more it feels like the only way to actually make the weight go away—the debt, the shame, the disappointment—is to just stop. to just make it all cease. it's the only thing that feels like it would actually solve the problem for everyone involved.",
